Class Student

com.example.ss7g7.stars.User
com.example.ss7g7.stars.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Student
extends User

Student Class

The Student class is a subclass of User It stores the details of a student.

Provides getters and setters to certain variables. Print functions to output data. Functions to add and remove courses. Functions to check if the new course from swapping or adding will clash with student's timetable.

2020/10/15
Version:
